  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK945">
<l>māṟupā ṭillāta uṇṭi maṟuttuṇṇi </l>
<l>ṉūṟupā ṭillai yuyirkku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>There will be no disaster to one's life if one eats with moderation, food that is not disagreeable.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
